<h2 id="metadata-frame-and-filter-menu">Metadata Frame and Filter Menu</h2>

<p>To facilitate the understanding that metadata is attached, not embedded, the metadata window is animated as a layer <em>on top of</em> the document.</p>

<p><img src="assets/4_taglinks_and_metadata.gif" alt="" /></p>

<p>Document and link metadata can be utilized for filtering.</p>

<p><img src="assets/5_basic_filtering.gif" alt="" /></p>

